#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A2A Java SDK 1.0.0.Beta1 Released"
msgstr "A2A Java SDK 1.0.0.Beta1发布"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A2A Java SDK 1.0.0.Beta1 is now available, aligned with the final A2A Specification 1.0.0."
msgstr "A2A Java SDK 1.0.0.Beta1 现已发布，与最终的 A2A 规范 1.0.0 保持一致。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We are pleased to announce the release of A2A Java SDK 1.0.0.Beta1, our first release fully aligned with the https://a2a-protocol.org/v1.0.0/specification/[final A2A Specification 1.0.0]. The A2A Protocol has reached stability as an open standard, and this release marks the Java SDK tracking that maturity: protocol conformance is the central focus, and the SDK coordinates now reflect the project's identity under the https://github.com/a2aproject[A2A Project organization]."
msgstr "我们很高兴地宣布 A2A Java SDK 1.0.0.Beta1 的发布，这是我们第一个与 link:https://a2a-protocol.org/v1.0.0/specification/[最终 A2A 规范 1.0.0] 完全一致的版本。 A2A 协议作为一个开放标准已经达到了稳定的状态，此次发布标志着 Java SDK 正在跟踪这一成熟度：协议一致性是核心重点，SDK 坐标现在反映了 link:https://github.com/a2aproject[A2A 项目组织] 下的项目身份。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As a sign of this maturity, two structural breaking changes accompany this release:"
msgstr "作为成熟的标志，此次发布的产品在结构上有两个突破性的变化："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Java packages have been renamed from `io.a2a.*` to `org.a2aproject.sdk.*`"
msgstr "Java 软件包已从 `io.a2a. **` *更名为org.a2aproject.sdk。*"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Maven `groupId` has changed from `io.github.a2asdk` to `org.a2aproject.sdk` (first introduced in 1.0.0.Alpha4)"
msgstr "Maven `groupId` 已从 `io.github.a2asdk` 更改为 `org.a2aproject.sdk` （在 1.0.0.Alpha4 中首次引入）。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What's A2A?"
msgstr "什么是 A2A？"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Agent2Agent (A2A) Protocol is an open standard that enables AI agents to communicate and collaborate with one another, regardless of each agent's underlying framework, language, or vendor. The A2A Java SDK makes it easy to build A2A-compliant agents in Java, with reference implementations based on Quarkus."
msgstr "Agent2Agent（A2A）协议是一项开放标准，它使人工智能代理能够相互通信和协作，而不受每个代理的底层框架、语言或供应商的影响。A2A Java SDK 可让您轻松地在 Java 中构建符合 A2A 协议的代理，并提供基于 Quarkus 的参考实现。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Breaking Changes"
msgstr "突破性变化"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
