msgstr "新 Maven 坐标"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Maven `groupId` has changed from `io.github.a2asdk` to `org.a2aproject.sdk`. If you are upgrading from any previous release, you must update your build files accordingly."
msgstr "Maven `groupId` 已从 `io.github.a2asdk` 更改为 `org.a2aproject.sdk` 。如果您是从之前的版本升级，则必须相应地更新您的构建文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The root artifact coordinates were renamed to reflect the project's new home under the https://github.com/a2aproject[A2A Project organization] and its availability on Maven Central."
msgstr "对根工件坐标进行了重命名，以反映项目在 link:https://github.com/a2aproject[A2A 项目组织] 下的新家及其在 Maven Central 上的可用性。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Update your `pom.xml` dependencies accordingly:"
msgstr "相应更新 `pom.xml` 依赖项："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "New Java Package Names"
msgstr "新 Java 软件包名称"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "All Java packages have been renamed from `io.a2a.*` to `org.a2aproject.sdk.*`. You must update all import statements in your source code when upgrading from any previous release."
msgstr "所有 Java 包已从 `io.a2a. **` *更名为org.a2aproject.sdk.* 。从以前的版本升级时，必须更新源代码中的所有导入语句。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Most IDEs can automate this migration via a project-wide find-and-replace of `io.a2a` → `org.a2aproject.sdk` in import statements, or by using the \"Optimize Imports\" / \"Migrate\" refactoring tools."
msgstr "大多数集成开发环境都可以通过在整个项目中查找并替换导入语句中的 `io.a2a` → `org.a2aproject.sdk` ，或使用 \"优化导入\"/\"迁移 \"重构工具来自动完成迁移。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Key Highlights in 1.0.0.Beta1"
msgstr "1.0.0.Beta1 中的主要亮点"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Equal Transport Support"
msgstr "平等交通支持"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "All three transports — JSON-RPC, gRPC, and HTTP+JSON/REST — are now fully supported and considered equal. Simply add the dependency for the transport you need (`a2a-java-sdk-reference-jsonrpc`, `a2a-java-sdk-reference-grpc`, or `a2a-java-sdk-reference-rest`) and the SDK will work seamlessly regardless of your choice."
msgstr "现在，JSON-RPC、gRPC 和 HTTP+JSON/REST 这三种传输方式都已完全支持，并被视为同等重要。只需添加您需要的传输的依赖关系 `（a2a-java-sdk-reference-jsonrpc` 、 `a2a` - `java` - `sdk` - `reference-grpc` 或 `a2a-java-sdk-reference-rest` ），无论您如何选择，SDK 都能无缝运行。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Structured Error Codes and Details"
msgstr "结构化错误代码和详细信息"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A2A error types now carry structured error codes and details, making error handling more precise and easier to integrate with observability tooling. Error responses also now use the correct `data` field name (previously `details`) in JSON/HTTP responses, in alignment with the specification."
msgstr "A2A 错误类型现在带有结构化的错误代码和详细信息，使错误处理更精确，也更容易与可观察性工具集成。错误响应现在也在 JSON/HTTP 响应中使用正确的 `数据字` 段名称（以前是 `详细信息` ），与规范保持一致。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "HTTP Caching Headers for Agent Card"
msgstr "代理卡的 HTTP 缓存标头"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Agent Card endpoint now returns proper HTTP caching headers, allowing clients and proxies to cache agent metadata efficiently and reduce unnecessary round trips."
msgstr "代理卡端点现在可以返回适当的 HTTP 缓存标头，允许客户端和代理高效地缓存代理元数据，减少不必要的往返。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`DataPart.fromJson()` Factory Method"
msgstr "`DataPart.fromJson()` 工厂方法"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A new `DataPart.fromJson()` factory method makes it straightforward to construct a `DataPart` from a raw JSON string, without requiring prior deserialization."
msgstr "新的 `DataPart.fromJson()` 工厂方法可直接从原始 JSON 字符串构建 `DataPart` ，而无需事先进行反序列化。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Flexible HTTP Client Support"
msgstr "灵活的 HTTP 客户端支持"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The SDK defaults to a `JdkA2AHttpClient` backed by the standard JDK `HttpClient`, suitable for any Java environment. The `HttpClient` builder also supports constructing a `JdkA2AHttpClient` from a prebuilt `HttpClient` instance, enabling advanced configuration scenarios such as custom SSL contexts or connection pool tuning."
msgstr "SDK 默认使用由标准 JDK `HttpClient` 支持的 `JdkA2AHttpClient` ，适用于任何 Java 环境。 `HttpClient` 生成器还支持从预建的 `HttpClient` 实例构建 `JdkA2AHttpClient` ，从而实现高级配置方案，如自定义 SSL 上下文或连接池调整。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When running on Quarkus, you can instead use the `VertxA2AHttpClient`, which is backed by the Vert.x HTTP client for better integration with Quarkus's reactive engine, connection management, and observability features."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 上运行时，可以使用 `VertxA2AHttpClient` ，它由 Vert.x HTTP 客户端提供支持，能更好地与 Quarkus 的反应式引擎、连接管理和可观察性功能集成。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Bug Fixes and Stability"
msgstr "错误修复和稳定性"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Terminal-state tasks now correctly reject further operations with `UnsupportedOperationError`"
msgstr "终端状态任务现在能在出现 `UnsupportedOperationError` 时正确拒绝进一步操作"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Race conditions in `EventConsumer` and the SSE transport have been resolved"
msgstr "`事件消费者` 和 SSE 传输中的竞赛条件已得到解决"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`PushNotificationNotSupportedError` now returns HTTP 501 as required by the specification"
msgstr "根据规范要求， `PushNotificationNotSupportedError` 现在会返回 HTTP 501"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "POST requests without a `Content-Type` header are now accepted when the body is empty"
msgstr "如果正文为空，现在可以接受不带 `Content-Type` 标头的 POST 请求"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Tenant and `protocolVersion` are now correctly preserved in the `ClientBuilder`"
msgstr "租户和 `协议版本` 现在可在 `客户端生成器` 中正确保存"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What's Next: Road to 1.0.0.GA"
msgstr "下一步计划通往 1.0.0.GA 的道路"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Before the 1.0.0.GA release, we plan to introduce the following:"
msgstr "在 1.0.0.GA 版本发布之前，我们计划引入以下内容："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Cross-version protocol support*: the SDK will be able to handle both version 1.0.0 and 0.3.0 of the A2A Protocol simultaneously, making it easier to interoperate with agents built against earlier versions of the specification."
msgstr "*跨版本协议支持* ：SDK 将能同时处理 A2A 协议的 1.0.0 版和 0.3.0 版，从而更容易与根据早期版本规范构建的代理进行互操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-27-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Specification micro-update tracking*: as the A2A Specification evolves with patch-level updates, the SDK will follow those changes promptly to remain fully conformant."
msgstr "*规范微更新跟踪* ：随着 A2A 规范的发展和补丁级更新，SDK 将及时跟踪这些变化，以保持完全一致。"

